description: UeMCCellProfile: Table storing UE (User Equipment) cell profile parameters for various cells, including filtering coefficients and measurement thresholds.  Columns: dateTime (timestamp), Area_Name (cell location), CellId (unique cell identifier), Id2 (duplicate of CellId), Id3 (likely an index), Id4 (profile identifier), vsDataType (data type identifier), vsDataFormatVersion (version), UeMCCellProfile.freqClassificationThreshold (frequency classification threshold), UeMCCellProfile.userLabel (user-defined label), UeMCCellProfile.filterCoefficientEUtraRsrp (filter coefficient for E-UTRA RSRP), UeMCCellProfile.filterCoefficientNrRsrqHigh (filter coefficient for NR RSRQ - high), UeMCCellProfile.sMeasure (signal measurement), UeMCCellProfile.filterCoefficientEUtraRsrq (filter coefficient for E-UTRA RSRQ), UeMCCellProfile.reservedBy (reserved field), UeMCCellProfile.filterCoefficientNrRsrpHigh (filter coefficient for NR RSRP - high), UeMCCellProfile.ueMCCellProfileId (UE cell profile ID), UeMCCellProfile.filterCoefficientNrRsrqLow (filter coefficient for NR RSRQ - low), UeMCCellProfile.filterCoefficientNrRsrpLow (filter coefficient for NR RSRP - low).
queries: Show me all UeMCCellProfile entries for Area_Name 'Downtown' where UeMCCellProfile.filterCoefficientNrRsrpHigh > 0.8.
What is the average UeMCCellProfile.freqClassificationThreshold for CellId 12345 between 2023-10-26 00:00:00 and 2023-10-27 00:00:00?
Retrieve UeMCCellProfile.filterCoefficientEUtraRsrp and UeMCCellProfile.filterCoefficientEUtraRsrq for all profiles with vsDataFormatVersion = 2.
Find all unique Area_Name values associated with UeMCCellProfile.userLabel = 'High Traffic'.
Give me a count of UeMCCellProfile entries where UeMCCellProfile.sMeasure is null and Area_Name starts with 'Suburb'.
